        properties:
            description: "Renly Baratheon was killed in his tent at Storm's End by a shadow creature birthed by Melisandre using Stannis's life force. Catelyn Stark and Brienne of Tarth were present. Brienne was falsely accused and fled with Catelyn."
            also_known_as: "Murder of Renly Baratheon"
